reviews.text: Old but well maintained mall with traditional Chinese outlets, supermarket, good range of local restaurants and wet market. Nice place to scroll around

Local neighbourhood mall equipped with grocery store, supermarket, chinese restaurant, fast food, food court, market, lifestyle household shops and even hairdresser/salon. You can basically find anything you need and satisfy all your needs for necessities and food, without the hassle to go back to the tai po central for all your wants.
